2.name: Message content rejected with comment
2.desc: Content of message is rejected, with comment.

3.name: Message content rejected without comment
3.desc: Content of message is rejected, without comment.

4.desc: Specified goods have been released from Customs control.

5.name: Goods required for examination
5.desc: Specified goods are required for examination.

6.name: All documents or as specified to be produced
6.desc: All document, or documents as specified, to be produced.

8.name: Goods may move under Customs transfer
8.desc: Specified goods may move under Customs transfer.

9.name: Declaration accepted awaiting goods arrival
9.desc: Goods declaration is accepted, awaiting goods arrival.

11.name: Pre-entry information
11.desc: Information for pre-entry of a goods declaration.

12.name: Sender not allowed the message type
12.desc: The sender is not allowed to send the message type which was sent.

13.name: Message type not supported
13.desc: The message type is not supported by the recipient.

14.name: Error message
14.desc: Message conveys information on an error.

15.name: Response after correction, correction approved
15.desc: Response after correction; correction has been approved.

16.name: Response after correction, correction non approved
16.desc: Response after correction; correction has not been approved.

18.name: Request for clearance
18.desc: Request for clearance of the goods.

20.name: Cash payment deferred
20.desc: Commercial transaction will be paid by cash within a prescribed time frame.

22.name: Export
22.desc: Goods are being taken out of the Customs territory.

23.name: Import
23.desc: Goods are being taken into a Customs territory.

24.name: Transit
24.desc: Goods are transported under Customs control from one Customs office to another.

25.name: Prohibited/restricted goods
25.desc: Goods are prohibited or restricted from import, export or transit by authority of Customs or another authority.

26.name: Container quarantine
26.desc: (4412) Specification of the status of the goods and of the transport equipment (container) and any packaging/dunnage with respect to quarantine restrictions.

27.name: Onward carriage: immediate export
27.desc: Movement type indicator: goods are being immediately taken out of the Customs territory.

28.name: Transhipment
28.desc: Goods are / are not to be transhipped at place of discharge/transhipment place.

29.name: Onward carriage: inland clearance
29.desc: Movement type indicator: goods are to move under Customs control to a Customs office where Customs formalities will be completed.

30.name: Transaction will not be processed until action is taken by sender

31.name: Transaction cannot be processed by the recipient
31.desc: Due to unknown reasons the transaction cannot be processed.

32.name: Transaction accepted
32.desc: This transaction is accepted by the recipient application and is a single transaction within a multiple transaction message.

33.name: Transaction rejected
33.desc: This transaction is rejected by the recipient application and is a single transaction within a multiple transaction message.

34.name: Transaction awaiting processing
34.desc: This transaction is waiting to be processed by the recipient application and is a single transaction within a multiple transaction message.

35.name: Transaction unknown
35.desc: This transaction is unknown by the recipient application and is a single transaction within a multiple transaction message.

36.name: Changed information
36.desc: Processing of information to note that only changes to existing data are transmitted.

37.name: Complete information
37.desc: Processing of information to note that complete data details (not just changes) are transmitted.

38.name: Manual procedures
38.desc: An automated process to revert to manual procedures.

39.name: Unrestow
39.desc: Reversal of a significant intentional restowage of cargo.

40.name: Seal intact
40.desc: Container seal is intact prior to unpacking.

41.name: Seal not intact
41.desc: Container seal is not intact prior to unpacking.

45.desc: The account number of the beneficiary is unknown.

46.name: Payee's account number unknown
46.desc: The account number of the payee is unknown.

47.name: Payor' account number unknown
47.desc: The account number of the payor is unknown.

48.name: Correspondent bank not possible
48.desc: The correspondent bank is not a possible one.

49.name: Execution date not possible
49.desc: The execution date cannot be met.

50.name: Value date not possible
50.desc: The value date cannot be met.

51.name: Currency code not possible
51.desc: The currency code does not exist.

52.name: Invalid decimal number
52.desc: The decimal number is not valid.

53.name: Orders executed (on)
53.desc: Confirmation that the orders have been executed.

54.name: Transaction(s) effected and advised (on)
54.desc: Confirmation that the transaction(s) has(ve) been effected and advised.

55.name: Not yet debited
55.desc: The amount(s) has(ve) not yet been debited.

56.name: Beneficiary is unable to identify the transaction
56.desc: The transaction cannot be identified by the beneficiary.

57.name: Restowage of cargo
57.desc: Intentional or unintentional restowage of cargo.

58.name: Onward carriage: sea clearance
58.desc: Movement type indicator: goods are to move under customs control, by sea, to a customs office where formalities will be completed.
